description: Full planning application for demolition and mixed use redevelopment of 735 dwellings comprising 95 houses and 640 apartments, retail (A1-A4) and commercial floorspace (B1 & D1), car parking, public open space, de-culverting of Pooles Sewer, alterations to access to New Road, closure of accesses to New Road and Bridge Road, formation of emergency-only access to Lamson Road.
